      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to see the \"transition\" part. it just feels like a mistake. like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. honestly, if that version of me is the only one people actually cared about, then the version that's left doesn't deserve to be here. it feels more honest to just... let go and be done with it.",
